name: HongMeng Series
description: Hongmeng is the undivided universe, the existence of no "time" in time and space, the vitality of all things in the universe, time and space, the origin of all concepts, and the original state of all time and space. The chaos of "Journey to the West" is not divided into chaos, and no one sees it. Since Pangu broke the Harmony, opened up a clear and turbid discernment. Everything starts here.
